	   <tr><td colspan=2>I had the same dilema when a higher level necro told me that i had to make it using my research skill.&nbsp;&nbsp;So here is what i did.<br><br>I went to the Bazaar and searched Words.  It brough all the words up for sale in the bazaar.  Turns out none of the Player vendors had any.  If that happens to you, don't worry.  Go to the NPC vendors in the center of the bazaar.  I found the two words i needed there.  The words needed for that spell (which is called animate dead) are Words of the Extinct and Words of the Quickening.  <br><br>Best of luck in your journeys and may you bring darkness upon all you touch.<br><br>Dijz,<br>Level 22 Minion of Doom<br>Saryrn<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
