	   <tr><td colspan=2>12 is very low for oasis. The random adds can be rally hard on you. I'd lvl in Nro, WC, or Befallen until you hit 14 or 15 (or get in a group in oasis).<br><br>If you insist on soloing in oasis, pull to the water's edge. You'll get less adds that way. When medding, go just offshore, and climb the pillars to sit and med. I've never had an aggro while on the pillars. In fact, you could actual park your pet near n the shore, and pull to that spot, then back up onto the pillar to dot/nuke, etc.<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
