	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, I found the spell....actually a good necro friend sold it to me for 50pp. On my server, BristleBane, this spell was selling somewhere between 500 and 1000pp!!!<br>Indeed a nice DOT to have for necros, but I don't think is worth paying that much.<br>For all those necros wanting to get this spell; make friends with high lvl necros and ask them 'nicely' to help you get it. I say ask them 'nicely', because it appears that some high lvl players think that low lvl players owe them some sort of respect, pffft. (Get a real life!)<br>If you try to hunt down the mobs that drop it, then you need a good group to hunt the mobs. By the way, you are most likely to find the spell by hunting Holgresh in Wakening Lands.<br><br>Anyways, that was what I did to get this spell, hope this helps to those of you trying to get this spell.<br><br>P.S. I did pay 700pp for my Summon Corpse spell :(&nbsp;&nbsp;, hehe<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
